A kindle information display that shows transit arrival times from the CTA, as well as weather information from wunderground.

Has multiple views for the weather: current conditions, hourly forecast for 12 hours, and a 5 day forecast.

kindleFrameApart.ai is an illustrator for a wooden frame that is lasercut, using 1/4inch wood. It worked successfully with an Epilog, but might require alterations for other laser cutters.

Based largely on the kindle-weather-display from:
http://www.mpetroff.net/archives/2012/09/14/kindle-weather-display/
